{"tid":1976213,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都係持續幾年瞓極唔夠好似好攰咁？","createTime":"2020-04-17T05:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T12:11:33.000Z","uid":325757,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6380e21f28f4c8076db39bed8629136d9ddd2827","tid":1976213,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"可以點改善 即使瞓咗成八九個鐘都係咁 一醒無幾耐就開始攰 好難集中精神，感覺只係身體仲識郁但係精神唔係全部都係曬度咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點改善 <br />\n唔知係咪因為成日只係淺層睡眠嘅關係<br />\n利申 好夜先瞓，但係以前就算好早瞓都係咁嘅樣<br />\n有無過來人分享下可以點改善"},{"pid":"9c84df39257ed10c11b65cb9b95d000883b10872","tid":1976213,"uid":123765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:50:09.000Z","msg":"仲以為係自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a3852e4251e0aa0b64dcefefe06dd8320452b3","tid":1976213,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:50:24.000Z","msg":"持續左30幾年"},{"pid":"21656423161c700c36196e2efd567096d2c2f779","tid":1976213,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24a3852e4251e0aa0b64dcefefe06dd8320452b3","tid":1976213,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:50:24.000Z","msg":"持續左30幾年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"都解決唔到？"},{"pid":"374f7a696273e4bd3afeb0a4a0016967b50f1c1b","tid":1976213,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c84df39257ed10c11b65cb9b95d000883b10872","tid":1976213,"uid":123765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:50:09.000Z","msg":"仲以為係自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:52:39.000Z","msg":"好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想個人精神啲都唔得"},{"pid":"c6767470dc5da82329db0ba887eb3d5f85f94c6a","tid":1976213,"uid":134636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05: